  <text>
    <body>
      <lg type="song lyrics">
        <head>Talk Talk Talk</head>
        <lg number="1" type="stanza">
          <l>Most of the people</l>
          <l>Talk talk talk</l>
          <l>Most of the people</l>
          <l>Are addicted to themselves</l>
          <l>Pretend they’re listening </l>
          <l>So they can go on</l>
          <l>Inventing answers for questions </l>
          <l>That you never had</l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="2" type="stanza">
          <l>Most of the people</l>
          <l>Block block block</l>
          <l>Most of the people</l>
          <l>Always seem to be o.k</l>
          <l>Go in go out just not to be alone</l>
          <l>And wake up tired knowing </l>
          <l>There is something they forget</l>
        </lg>
        <lg Chorus="yes" number="3" type="stanza">
          <l>Just make some waves</l>
          <l>Create a buzz</l>
          <l>You should be fine</l>
          <l>If not come back</l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="4" type="stanza">
          <l>Most of the people</l>
          <l>Want more more more</l>
          <l>Of no matter what no matter why </l>
          <l>No matter where</l>
          <l>Most of the people</l>
          <l>Talk talk talk</l>
          <l>Most of the people</l>
          <l>Are addicted</l>
        </lg>
        <lg Chorus="yes" number="5" type="stanza">
          <l>Just make some waves</l>
          <l>Create a buzz</l>
          <l>You should be fine</l>
          <l>If not come back</l>
        </lg>
      </lg>
    </body>
